Package: datapackage.parquet
Type: Package
Title: Data Reader for Parquet Files for the Datapackage Package
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Jan",
           family = "van der Laan",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "r@eoos.dds.nl",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0693-1514"))
Description: Adds a reader and writer for parquet files to the datapackage
    package. Loading the package allows one to automatically read parquet files
    in Data Resources. It is also possible to request an Arrow connection to
    the data.
Depends:
    datapackage,
    R (>= 4.2.0)
Imports:
    arrow
Suggests:
    simplermarkdown,
    dplyr
VignetteBuilder: simplermarkdown
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
